Package: ediblecity
Type: Package
Title: Modeling Urban Agriculture at City Scale
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Josep Pueyo-Ros
Maintainer: Josep Pueyo-Ros <jospueyo@gmail.com>
Description: The purpose of this package is to estimate the potential of urban agriculture to contribute to addressing several urban challenges at the city-scale. Within this aim, we selected 8 indicators directly related to one or several urban challenges. Also, a function is provided to compute new scenarios of urban agriculture.
